{"tid":2437763,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"瞎毀！ 台中公益路跑 送「慶記」保溫杯","createTime":"2021-03-08T05:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T06:33:17.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"efd25332d86c301e21db775bb65e4da92a507f12","tid":2437763,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/03/08/103.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F03%2F08%2F103.jpg&h=bb8d1fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MPB5N5n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMPB5N5n.jpg&h=c11f9165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台中市電腦商業同業公會昨天主辦「台中資訊盃公益路跑」，<br />\n吸引上千人參加，參賽民眾每人都可拿到一個子彈造型的保溫杯，因台中市曾被稱為是「<br />\n慶記」（台語子彈之意）之都，部分民眾在臉書笑稱「拿到台中特產一枚」、「是故意的<br />\n嗎？」主辦單位則澄清，因原本規劃活動要跑進成功嶺營區，為配合軍方意象才會設計子<br />\n彈造型保溫杯，沒有其他用意。<br />\n <br />\n由台中市電腦商業同業公會主辦，並由台灣大腳丫長跑協會承辦的「台中資訊盃公益路跑<br />\n」，昨天早上6點從烏日高鐵東路的起點鳴槍開跑，吸引上千位民眾參加，並有趣味造型<br />\n獎比賽 ，許多跑者都挖空心思打扮，有人著軍服扛木槍，也有人穿短裙，還有3位女跑者<br />\n穿旗袍跑42公里全馬，整場賽事彷彿嘉年華會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/Taichung/paper/1435520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2FTaichung%2Fpaper%2F1435520&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058oaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=812a2dbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2FTaichung%2Fpaper%2F1435520&h=7b74ce05\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/Taichung/paper/1435520</a>"},{"pid":"f48a5c6cb8d850b6eb190c870737ed0ce0f4f7b7","tid":2437763,"uid":10890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:38:56.000Z","msg":"台中冇人揸車會呠人<br />\n被人呠就請佢食慶記<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dca85d95abb34a1300e8c4ad45195213a327a93","tid":2437763,"uid":32511,"like":3,"di